    Note:
    MIPS Linux MAP_FIXED constant.
    Source: Linux kernel arch/mips/include/uapi/asm/mman.h
    (#define MAP_FIXED 0x10).  MAP_FIXED instructs mmap to place the
    mapping at the exact addr supplied; failure if that range cannot
