    :End Note
    Return 16
End Process

Note: File mode constants (POSIX permission bits)
Process called "mips64_MODE_0644" returns Integer:
    Note:
    POSIX file mode 0644 = rw-r--r-- (owner read/write, group/other read).
    Octal 0644 = decimal 420 = 0x1A4 = S_IRUSR | S_IWUSR | S_IRGRP | S_IROTH.
    Source: POSIX <sys/stat.h>; identical across MIPS Linux and asm-generic.
    :End Note
    Return 420
End Process

Process called "mips64_MODE_0755" returns Integer:
    Note:
    POSIX file mode 0755 = rwxr-xr-x (owner all, group/other read+execute).
    Octal 0755 = decimal 493 = 0x1ED = S_IRWXU | S_IRGRP | S_IXGRP | S_IROTH | S_IXOTH.
    Source: POSIX <sys/stat.h>; identical across MIPS Linux and asm-generic.
    :End Note
    Return 493
End Process

