Note: Generic syscall wrappers using inline assembly
Process called "mips64_syscall_0" takes syscall_number as Integer returns Integer:
    Let result be 0
    Inline Assembly:
        li $v0, syscall_number
        syscall
        move result, $v0
    End Assembly
    Return result
End Process

